716672f-c.text:
(1)
Bennett Ave., west side, north from, but not including 192nd Street. Notice the subway tunnel entrance in the side of the cliff.
November 23, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, from a different angle. The stone buildings on the top of the cliff, are between Bennett and Fort Washington Aves. (at 192nd
Street).
November 23, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
(3)
The cliff from a point further northward, showing the tunnel entrance in the background.
November 23, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
